This method define the path to the epJSON file.

Args:
    env_config (dict): Environment configuration.

Return:
    dict: The method returns the env_config with modifications.

Example:

    env_config = {
        ...
        'episode_config': {
            'epjson_files_folder_path': 'path/to/epjson/files',
            'id_epjson_file': None
        }
    }
